name: PassiveExpiringMap_getTest
description: Unit tests for the get method of PassiveExpiringMap, testing scenarios where entries exist and are not expired, exist but are expired, and do not exist.

test_cases.name: testGet_EntryExistsAndNotExpired
test_cases.description: Tests the get method when an entry exists and is not expired.

test_cases.name: testGet_EntryExistsButExpired
test_cases.description: Tests the get method when an entry exists but is expired.

test_cases.name: testGet_EntryDoesNotExist
test_cases.description: Tests the get method when an entry does not exist.
